# 8bytedining

8bytedining is a simple API allowing consumers to retreave information about recipes, cuisines, and ingredents.

# Group Recipes

Resources related to recipes in the API.


## Recipes [api/Recipes/{recipe_id}]

A recipe object has the following attributes:

+ Parameters
    + id(required, string, 'barley-risotto') ... String id of the recipe to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a Recipe [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    [
      {
        "name": "Barley Risotto",
        "id": "barley-risotto",
        "url": "https://api.pearson.com/kitchen-manager/v1/recipes/barley-risotto",
        "cuisine": "Italian",
        "cooking_method": "Risotto method",
        "ingredients": [
        "barley",
        "water",
        "butter",
        "garlic clove",
        "Chicken Stock",
        "green onion",
        "asiago cheese",
        "kosher salt",
        "ground black pepper"
        ],
        "image": "https://api.pearson.com/kitchen-manager/v1/images/full/defaultrecipe.jpg",
        "thumb": "https://api.pearson.com/kitchen-manager/v1/images/thumbs/defaultrecipe.jpg"
       }
       { 
         "etc...."
        }
    ]

Returns a json file with recipes similar in ingredient to the specified recipe
## Similar recipes [api/Recipes/?similar={True}?id={recipe_id}]

