#Group Cusine

Resources related to ingredients in the API.


## Cusines [api/cusines/{cusinieID}]

A Cusines object has the following attributes:

+ Parameters
    + cusinieID (required, string, 'African') ... string 'cusinieID' of the cusinieID to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a Cusine [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    [
      {
        "name": "African",
        "id": "african",
        "url": "https://api.pearson.com/kitchen-manager/v1/cuisines/african",
        "recipe_count": 0
      },
      {
        "more cusines..."
      }
    ]

Returns a json with recipes of the given cuisinie and that fall within the specified price range.
## Cusines Range [api/cusines/cusinie={cusinie_id}?offset={offset}&limit={limit}]
A Price Range object has the following attributes:

+ Parameters
    + cusinie (required, string, 'Mexican') ... string 'cusinie' required to specify the cusinie. Has example value.
    + offset(not required, number, '1') ... number 'offset' of the cusinie price to perform action with. Has example value.
    + limit(required, number, '10') ... number 'limit' of the cusinie price to perform actiion with. Has example value.
